@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jjmxqi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.07) + wp.cos(v2))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = (wp.cos(v1) * (tmp + v0))
    v2 = v0
    tmp = ((v2 - v0) - wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.74)))
    data[tid] = v0
